snippet.title: Still be a Human (trailer)
snippet.description:
steam free demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1896810/Still_be_a_Human/?beta=0

Still be a Human is an Roguelike Action in which you have to descend from the top of the Tower of Shadows, a cult who sacrificed their lives to gain immortality in the form of a shadow. Combine found artifacts by placing them in abilities and find out can you Still be a Human.
